{"tid":379918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門消息：天鴿吹襲1名退役駐澳門匪軍滑倒身亡","createTime":"2017-08-29T17:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T03:16:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c59800e7879d9bc9e4169425606613f002e97f","tid":379918,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/photo/bkn-20170829155548824-0829_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170829230259\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829155548824-0829_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170829230259&h=7314ae24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n颱風「天鴿」上周吹襲澳門，造成至少10人喪生，其中一名死者為30歲持本地藍卡的男子，因被風吹至滑倒撞牆不治，今(29日)證實為駐澳部隊退役軍人阮班貴。<br />\n<br />\n阮為湖北黃石人，於2006年12月至2011年12月在駐澳部隊服役5年，為一級士官，於澳門回歸10周年時曾獲許三等功嘉獎，而他退役後留澳工作，於澳門日光設施及物業管理有限公司擔任主管。阮班貴不幸離世，留下遺孀、4歲幼子及多病的父母。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上周二(22日)天鴿吹襲澳門的前一天，阮班貴通宵值班候命，於翌日(23日)下班後，在等待回珠海期間，強風突然加大，阮的公司因人手不足以應對突發災害，阮自發無條件往增援日升樓及房屋局湖畔辦事處，調配應急物資於各個場所進行防風，並進行安全巡查，期間阮班貴被強風吹倒致頭部受撞擊重創，經搶救後不治。而事發前阮曾與妻子和兒子視頻通話報平安，可惜那一通話已是他與妻兒的最後一次見面。<br />\n<br />\n阮班貴的離去讓親友們痛心，本月26日下午他的遺體運返珠海，其父撫棺哽咽的情景讓在場人士忍不住哭泣。阮妻稱，丈夫人品好，在家從不讓她和媽媽做任何家務。阮班貴的兒子形容爸爸像超級英雄，無所畏懼、無所不能，而為不讓父親的辭世為兒子成長帶來陰影，家人只告訴他爸爸要出差很長一段時間。阮的同事憶述，工作中無論甚麼事情，阮回應最多的就是「好，沒問題」，且從不拒絕任務，任何事情都敢於承擔，是一位難得的好同事、好兄弟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/photo/bkn-20170829155548824-0829_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170829230259\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829155548824-0829_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170829230259&h=2b0a070c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170829/photo/bkn-20170829155548824-0829_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170829230259\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170829%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170829155548824-0829_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170829230259&h=aa2f622b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a31d24f5cc3c0b8426425cba85f5a9c4ba6f190","tid":379918,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c143c4a02c637a7d55230c2d20bedc8a7bda5491","tid":379918,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"咁就死 豆腐做嫁"},{"pid":"dc91074c5776283cfe3cf4223f8c9d11cfe097d5","tid":379918,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:28:33.000Z","msg":"駐港解放軍退役後有冇得留低香港做嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08529ae095825abdd6178a039c31c36709db4762","tid":379918,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d922d5c6ad2bd00467fa2eefbe97a2daff2670b","tid":379918,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:42:51.000Z","msg":"滑到身亡,周星馳電影咁諗起都好笑"},{"pid":"0299605d893a056f4b9073d2d7ad54e8a0fd5d1c","tid":379918,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:46:40.000Z","msg":"福氣"},{"pid":"cb0aaed01cc7b3e29cca9093abc87bbe6caf08c9","tid":379918,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"梁烈唯.jpg"},{"pid":"452bd0b0e7f84da07d6479c4904aebc077a2fe8d","tid":379918,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"滑倒再撞牆死，呢個世界有幾多個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係嚟串鳩佢哋，認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3b014041d5eb46d79